Use the `nextjs-react-conventions` skill.

## Commands
- **Build**: `npm run build`
- **Lint**: `npm run lint`
- **Test all**: `CI_ENV=BITBUCKET npm run test`
- **Test single file**: `npm test -- src/__tests__/path/to/test.tsx`
- **Test coverage**: `npm run coverage`

NEVER run dev server unless explicitly told to do so.
